reviewText: I purchased this as a gift for my Son.  So I was surprised when he left me a message that he received it and it had a rattle inside the package.  When he opened it,  it was labeled damaged but they sent it out anyway.  How disappointed I was, this dvd wasn't cheap. So we will see how quick they replace it
Pretty complete DVD guide.  If you are new to K10D...this should be necessary item.  Well done.
